{"title":"白衣——献给一位牺牲的女医生","authors":["许向诚"],"dates":[{"year":2003,"month":5,"day":31}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"白衣"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——献给一位牺牲的女医生"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"许向诚"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有一叶白帆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"袅动着爱神的翅膀"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无论大海多宽"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"岸  总是在帆的下面"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有一朵白云"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让我久久地仰视"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在她清丽的边缘"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那片天空最蓝最蓝"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有一只白鸽"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"衔来热烈的花朵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为了节日的母亲不再忧伤"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"日夜忙碌  默默啼血"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有一檐白雪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"落满鸟儿们的泥爪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"檐雪滴响了时钟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鸟儿们向着太阳飞去"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有一丛白荷"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁在丝雨中与甘露同眠"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只有女神的睡姿"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"才能如此美丽  端庄  安详"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有一件白衣"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"遗物的白衣"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"被一个圣洁的灵魂披上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呼吸着大风舞蹈"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我愿用我的哭声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为她伴唱"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":7,"page_end":7}